title: Power4Patriots
description:
This is the entire Power4Patriots.com platinum package, including all .pdf files and videos, Plus the following Bonuses in PDF, Word, and Excel: Disaster 101, Solar Packs, Home Energy Audit, and Water Survival. Learn to Survive before the SHTF!

Solar Power Pack: Six professionally produced easy-to-follow videos along with two fully-illustrated companion manuals that will show you step-by-step how to build your own solar power system that can save you thousands on your energy bills.

Wind Power Pack: Four professional-quality videos along with two more fully-illustrated manuals that will show you how to build a simple, durable wind turbine for the fraction of the cost of a pre-fab system.

Solar Hot Water Guide: A complete illustrated guide to building and installing your own solar hot water heater. Your family will be able to rely on the comfort of abundant hot water without paying through the nose.

Solar Heating Guide: Using the power of the sun to heat your home is easier than you might think, and this detailed introduction will show you how!

Enjoy!
